</line><line>Edgeworth:
Detective, I have a favor to ask of you. We would like for you to bring Missile to the prison courtyard.
</line><line>Gumshoe:
<textEffects>Sounds like you need the help of one of my "Seven Secret Weapons" again, huh, sir?</textEffects>
</line><line>Edgeworth:
<textEffects>(I thought Missile belonged to the police department.)</textEffects> And also, I would like for you to contact a witness. Please contact Regina Berry of the Berry Big Circus and bring her here.
</line><line>Gumshoe:
<textEffects>Roger that, sir! I'll bring them over in a flash!</textEffects>
</line><line>Kay:
So, what should we do while we wait for Gummy? How about some hide-and-seek?
</line><line>Ray:
What are you talking about, Kay? There's nowhere to hide here.
</line><line>Edgeworth:
<textEffects>(I don't think that is the issue.)</textEffects> Kay. During times like this, isn't it your turn to shine?
</line><line>Kay:
Oh, that! You want me to re-create the crime scene!
